name: Speedrent Technology Sdn Bhd
description: Developer of a real estate platform designed to assist owners in managing tenants and properties at an affordable rate. The company's platform has a searchable database that lets users find homes and deal with landlords directly, enabling landlords to rent properties in a cheaper, faster, and easier way.
